0e7eada, \u00c7anakkale.\n* {{cite book\n| last                  = \u0391\u03bb\u03b5\u03be\u03ac\u03bd\u03b4\u03c1\u03bf\u03c5\n| first                 = \u0394\u03b7\u03bc\u03ae\u03c4\u03c1\u03b7\u03c2\n| title                 = \u038a\u03bc\u03b2\u03c1\u03b9\u03bf\u03b9-\u03a4\u03b5\u03bd\u03ad\u03b4\u03b9\u03bf\u03b9 \u039f\u0399 \u0395\u039b\u039b\u0397\u039d\u0395\u03a3 \u03a0\u039f\u03a5 \u039e\u0395\u03a7\u0391\u03a3\u0391\u039c\u0395\n| publisher             = \u0395\u03c1\u03c9\u03b4\u03b9\u03cc\u03c2\n| year                  = 2002\n| isbn                  = 978-960-7942-37-1\n}}\n\n==External links==\n*[http://www.bozcaada.gov.tr/ Bozcaada government website] (Turkish)\n*[http://www.bozcaadamuzesi.net/ Bozcaada Museum (private)] (Turkish)\n*[https://www.nytimes.com/slideshow/2012/07/08/travel/08BOZCAADA.html Bozcaada slide show from New York Times Travel section]\n*{{Wikivoyage-inline|Bozcaada}}\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20121017181929/http://en.bozcaadarehberi.com/ Bozcaada Guide]\n*[http://wn.com/la_Tenedos#/videos Une fin de semaine sur l'ile de Bozcaada] (slide show)\n*[http://www.bozcaada.bel.tr/ Website, Municipality of Bozcaada] (Turkish)\n\n{{Aegean Sea}}\n{{Islands of Turkey}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n[[Category:History of Turkey]]\n[[Category:Islands of Turkey]]\n[[Category:Greece\u2013Turkey relations]]\n[[Category:Human rights abuses]]\n[[Category:Discrimination in Turkey]]\n[[Category:Persecution of Greeks in Turkey]]\n[[Category:Ancient Greek archaeological sites in Turkey]]\n[[Category:North Aegean islands]]\n[[Category:Locations in the Iliad]]\n[[Category:Tenea]]\n[[Category:Tenedos| ]]\n[[Category:Fishing communities in Turkey]]\n[[Category:Bozcaada district]]\n[[Category:Islands of \u00c7anakkale Province]]\n[[Category:Members of the Delian League]]\n[[Category:Populated places in the ancient Aegean islands]]\n[[Category:Populated places in ancient Troad]]\n[[Category:Greek city-states]]\n", "text_old": "{{Other uses}}\n{{redire